			<CASNumber>10101-63-0</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Lead iodide, also known as plumbous iodide, is a bright yellow odourless crystalline solid at room temperature that turns orange and crimson when heated. It is a significant chemical substance with various applications, including the production of solar cells. Lead iodide is produced by reacting potassium iodide with lead nitrate, resulting in a chemical equation: Pb(NO3)2 + 2 KI → PbI2 + 2 KNO3. It is used in metal halide perovskite semiconductors for solar cells, often leading to improved performance.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">碘化铅，也称为碘化亚铅，在室温下是一种亮黄色无味的晶体固体，加热后会变成橙色和深红色。它是一种重要的化学物质，具有多种应用，包括太阳能电池的生产。碘化铅是由碘化钾和硝酸铅反应产生的，得到一个化学方程式：Pb（NO3）2+2 KI→ PbI2+2 KNO3。它被用于太阳能电池的金属卤化物钙钛矿半导体，通常可以提高性能。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>PbI2</sumFormula>
